Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.33,0:16:18.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,即Rallston愿意收留他  可宿舍暑假不开放\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Even if Rallston would take him,the dorms are closed for the summer.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.94,0:16:21.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,最近的汽车旅馆到这里也有30英里的路程\N{\fscx070\fscy070}The nearest motel is 30 miles away,Your Honor,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.74,0:16:24.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,他的驾照也被吊销了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}and his driver's license has been revoked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.18,0:16:27.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,事实上 我们车库楼上有个房间\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Actually,we have a room above our garage.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:31.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,他可以付房租\N{\fscx070\fscy070}The boy could pay rent.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:35.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得可以  你呢 律师\N{\fscx070\fscy070}It works for me. How about you,Counselor?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.89,0:16:38.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我们也可以接受 法官大人\N{\fscx070\fscy070}That's acceptable to us as well,Your Honor.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:48.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,又个给Cavanaugh 家惹事的Rallston男孩\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Another Rallston boy takes a bite out of the Cavanaugh family.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.83,0:16:52.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我跟这件事没关系 说实话 我都不在场\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I had nothing to do with this one. I wasn't even here. Exactly.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.10,0:16:54.94,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你...我没责怪任何人\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You... Nobody's blaming anybody.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:56.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,如果你一开始给我打电话就好了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}It would have been nice if one of you'd called me{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在刚出问题的时候\N{\fscx070\fscy070}when the trouble first started.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Jesse跟Alice是在这里刻的字\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I remember when Jesse and Alice carved this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:09.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,妈 还记得你跟我说过很多次吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Mom,remember what you said to me so many times?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.22,0:17:11.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,留得青山在 不怕没柴烧 对吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}As long as we're all alive,it's nothing more than a bad day. Right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.99,0:17:14.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,对呀 这一切都会过去的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Yeah. We can beat a bad day. Right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:17.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,唉 对啊\N{\fscx070\fscy070} Right.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:26.60,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,他们来了!他们来了!\N{\fscx070\fscy070}They're here! They're here!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.02,0:17:41.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为他对我们的出价不满意\N{\fscx070\fscy070}That's because he doesn't like the percentage we're offering.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.49,0:17:43.75,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,他得想出好点的主意才行\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Then he's gonna have to come up with a better deal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:46.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,这很关键 对 我得挂了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}It's a matter... Yeah. I gotta go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:50.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,听着 我跟交代了所有事情 包括你的午餐\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Listen,I worked everything out with these people,including your meals.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:54.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你就只需要些零花钱\N{\fscx070\fscy070}So all you're gonna need is some spending money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:58.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,这些够撑一段时间了 如果不够的话\N{\fscx070\fscy070}This should last you for a while,but if you need some more,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,就打我办公室的电话\N{\fscx070\fscy070}you just call my office.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.94,0:18:05.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,后面几星期你可能很难见到我 嗯\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- I'm gonna be a little hard to reach for the next few weeks. - Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:07.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,嗨 你们好啊 -下午好\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Hello there. - Good afternoon.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.61,0:18:12.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我来不及了了 还要赶一架航班\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Hey. I'm running a little late,and I have a flight to catch,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我想应该没什么问题了吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}so I assume there's nothing else we need to discuss.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:17.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我们没问题了 \N{\fscx070\fscy070} No. I think we're good..{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:25.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果想参观的话 你房间在车库楼上右侧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Your room's right above the garage if you want to go up.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.86,0:18:27.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,记住我的话 \N{\fscx070\fscy070}Now,you remember what I told you..{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:30.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把重心放在有意义的事情上\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Keep your eyes forward on the important things.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.47,0:18:32.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Yes,sir.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.60,0:19:05.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,它叫Ralph.\N{\fscx070\fscy070}That's Ralph.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:07.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,它也住这里\N{\fscx070\fscy070}He lives here too.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:11.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,真是好极了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Perfect.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我给他送点上去\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Maybe I should take him up a plate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:23.11,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我们都喂到嘴边了 他饿了会下来吃的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Honey,we offered. When he gets hungry,he'll come down.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:26.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,做了那么多缺德事 让他饿死算了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Let him starve. After everything he did.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.59,0:19:31.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,当时到底是几辆车在乱跑\N{\fscx070\fscy070}How many cars were in that race,anyway?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:38.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- 两辆 - 难道他一个人骑两辆吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Two. - Was he driving both of them?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.77,0:19:44.07,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得他挺帅的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I think he's hot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:27.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我爹准备让我修篱笆桩修到90岁\N{\fscx070\fscy070}My dad's already got me fixing fence posts till I'm 90.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:29.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,包括重建Mable \N{\fscx070\fscy070}Plus the work at Mable's..{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.24,0:20:32.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你不生我的气 我的麻烦也够多的了 \N{\fscx070\fscy070}I got enough problems without you being mad at me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:35.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我只是觉得你可以更大方些的 仅此而已\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I just think you could have been the bigger man. That's all.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.83,0:20:39.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}All right. Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.70,0:20:47.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,那 我们之间没什么问题了吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Well. Is everything still okay with us?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:54.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,天哪 我们几百年没这么干了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}God,we haven't done that in about a hundred years.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:07.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你从来没有吹好过\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You were never very good at that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.59,0:21:09.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,哈 这可是我教你的啊\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Ah,but I'm the one that taught you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:12.32,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,可只有我掌握了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- I'm the one that mastered it. - [Sputtering]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.94,0:21:28.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,该起床了 富二代 去给奶牛挤奶去\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Time to get up,Richie. Gotta evacuate the cows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:31.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,是煤气中毒还是怎么了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Is there a gas leak or something?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,挤奶啊\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Evacuating.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:40.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,如果你认为我会碰这些东西 那你就是疯了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You're out of your mind if you think I'm touchin' that thing.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:49.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,早上好\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Well,good morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:55.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- 要吃什么吗 早务后有早餐\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Can I fix you something? - Breakfast is served after morning chores.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我不吃早餐\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I don't eat breakfast{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.91,0:22:00.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想知道我们什么时候去干活\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I was just coming in to find out when we leave for work.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.75,0:22:02.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,20分钟后到卡车那去\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Be at the truck in 20 minutes.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.23,0:22:24.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-你不累吗富二代  -不\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Not getting tired,are you,Richie? - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:29.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,在你爱抚那些奶牛时我去补了一个小时的觉\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Got an extra hour's sleep while you were fondling your cows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:31.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,午餐好了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}[Mr. Arnold] That's lunch!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.91,0:22:35.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,伙计们 休息时间 吃的跟饮料在冷藏室里\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Break time,guys. Food and drink's in the cooler.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.48,0:22:37.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我自己有午饭吃\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I'll get my own lunch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.48,0:22:41.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,随便你  午饭啊 一起去吃吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Suit yourself. Lunch! Let's go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.89,0:22:45.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我走了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Okay,I'm outta here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.46,0:22:47.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,当你爸真好\N{\fscx070\fscy070}-  - Good to be your father.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.46,0:22:49.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,当你女儿真好\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Good to be your daughter.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.73,0:22:53.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,妈 你知道我昨晚在想什么吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Do you know what I was thinking about last night,Mom? - What?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:57.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,他们会给我们钱重建对吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}They're giving us all this money to rebuild. Right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:22:59.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以从头开始 好好玩玩\N{\fscx070\fscy070}So we can start all over from scratch and have fun.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:01.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以去古董店\N{\fscx070\fscy070}We can go to antique stores...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:03.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,或者是跳蚤市场弄些时髦的家具\N{\fscx070\fscy070}and flea markets and get funky furniture.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:06.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 去Falco医生那里后再去\N{\fscx070\fscy070}We could do that. We could stop on the way back from Dr. Falco's.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.91,0:23:10.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了这件事了\N{\fscx070\fscy070} I completely forgot about Dr. Falco.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.11,0:23:14.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,这是个好迹象 我想你的膝盖应该好多了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}That's a good sign. I guess your knee hasn't been bothering you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.09,0:23:16.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,妈 我的膝盖很好\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Mom,my knee's fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.09,0:23:19.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,那我能取消预约吗 -不行\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- So can I cancel Dr. Falco? - No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:24.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌 -我知道\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Oh,I hate this. - I know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.23,0:23:27.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,他只是想确认你真的完全康复了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}He's just making sure everything's still okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:30.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我的膝盖没事 为什么我们老是来这里啊\N{\fscx070\fscy070}My knee's fine. Why do we have to keep coming here?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.20,0:23:33.14,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是医生的要求 -Samantha\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Because the doctor said so. - Samantha?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.61,0:23:44.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,当一些事物从我们身边被夺走\N{\fscx070\fscy070}When something is taken away from us so violently,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.82,0:23:46.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,就像是发生在Mable餐厅的火灾\N{\fscx070\fscy070}like the recent fire at Mable's Table,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.05,0:23:50.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我们不禁要扪心自问\N{\fscx070\fscy070}we are forced to ask questions.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.35,0:23:53.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,这仅仅只是个糟糕的事件吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Was it simply a terrible accident?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:56.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,就像是两个原子之间任意的碰撞\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Atoms colliding at random?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.36,0:23:59.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是是年轻人做出了错误选择的结果\N{\fscx070\fscy070}A result of young people making poor choices?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.03,0:24:02.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,还是因为这是上帝…\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Or was it the hand of God...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.70,0:24:07.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,他给我们制定的人生大计划中的一小部分\N{\fscx070\fscy070}a part of a larger plan that He might have for us?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.58,0:24:12.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Jasper你基友Kelly今天去哪了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Hey,Jasper. Where's your new pal Kelley today?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.61,0:24:14.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,哦他在你房间里 跟你老妈搞着呢\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Oh,he's at your house,getting busy with your mom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.78,0:24:17.10,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 昨晚我跟你妈一起 \N{\fscx070\fscy070}Really? 'Cause last night when I was with your mom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.10,0:24:18.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妈还说他可爱\N{\fscx070\fscy070},she said he was kind of cute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.48,0:24:21.25,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-我快嫉妒疯了-别说了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}It made me jealous. Enough with the mother thing already.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.32,0:24:23.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- 我同意 - 不好意思\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- I second that. - Excuse me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.42,0:24:26.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我受够了这些话题了 我还蛮喜欢你妈妈的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}What? I'm just saying enough's enough. I like your mom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.42,0:24:30.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,各位 我们今晚要去裸泳 想去吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Hey,guys. We're goin' skinny dipping tonight. Wanna come?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.29,0:24:33.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我爸让我工作呢 我的男人不穿衣服时可帅了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Dad's making me work. - My man looks good naked.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.00,0:24:35.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我喜欢人猿泰山\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- - Yeah,I'm like Tarzan.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.57,0:24:41.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-一会见好吗 -嗯哼\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- See you later? - Mm-hmm.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.33,0:25:46.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,下午好 各位同学 嘉宾们\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Good afternoon,classmates and invited guests.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.70,0:25:50.57,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,今天我们要给我们的幼儿时代\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Today we mark the end of our infancy,{\r}
