Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.11,0:25:58.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,作为毕业生 我们满怀希望期待未来\N{\fscx070\fscy070}As new graduates we look forward with hope to the future,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.75,0:26:01.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,不久后未来也变成了过去\N{\fscx070\fscy070}and then the future becomes the past.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.42,0:26:04.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我们生活有意义吗 \N{\fscx070\fscy070}At what point in our lives {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.62,0:26:07.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有思考过我们的过去及未来吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}do we begin thinking about the past and the future?\N{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.49,0:26:11.05,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,当我还是个孩子的时候 我没怎么考虑过这些\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I know when I was a child I never gave them much thought.{\r}
