Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.30,0:26:18.97,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Robert Frost曾写过他那无忧无虑的童年\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Robert Frost once wrote about his carefree youth{\r}
