Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.92,0:28:15.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,噢哦 我的孙女好吗 太想念这里的午餐了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Whoa. How's my girl? - Earl,missin' a great lunch here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.29,0:28:17.22,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,来把她给我抱吧 -我们这里吃的多得是\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- I'll catch up. - We have tons of food,baby.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.79,0:28:23.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Jo 很感激你们提供这些食物 谢谢你们\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Jo,appreciate this. Thank you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.86,0:28:26.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你们工作那么幸苦 这是应该的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You guys have been working so hard,you deserve it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.46,0:28:28.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Sam去哪了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Where's Sam?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.52,0:28:46.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我不会告诉其他人你吃过了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Don't worry,I won't tell anybody you actually ate.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.36,0:28:55.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你别总是那副不高兴的样子\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I'd like it if you'd stop sulking long enough to try.{\r}
