Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.27,0:29:05.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你就像个大孩子一样坐在这里\N{\fscx070\fscy070}And you decide to sit out here like a really big baby.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.34,0:29:10.26,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,因为我给你这种印象\N{\fscx070\fscy070}And at what point did I give you the impression {\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.26,0:29:54.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就可以跑来这羞辱我了吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070} that it was okay to come out here and insult me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.32,0:29:56.51,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,离Samantha远点\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Stay away from Samantha.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.59,0:29:59.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,放轻松 我没有对你女朋友下手\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Relax. I'm not makin' a move on your girlfriend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.89,0:30:03.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-你认为我担心的是这个-不知道 不关心\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- You think I'm worried about that? - Don't know,don't care.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.86,0:30:06.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,离她远点\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Stay away from her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.93,0:30:09.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,哦 那你又想怎样\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Or what,exactly?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.63,0:30:12.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,听着 富二代 别把我惹毛了 知道吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Listen,Richie. You don't want to mess with me. All right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.44,0:30:15.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 好怕怕\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Ooh. Scary.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.37,0:30:17.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,真是惊讶,你还担心女朋友啊\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I'm surprised you even bother with a girlfriend{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.54,0:30:20.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你对付那些母牛那么有一手\N{\fscx070\fscy070}you got such a good thing with those cows.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.18,0:30:22.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你什么意思  哦 承认吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- What's that supposed to mean? - Aw,come on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.15,0:30:24.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你在那牛圈里妻妾成群\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You got yourself a regular harem out there.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.68,0:30:26.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上掀开她们的裙子 \N{\fscx070\fscy070}Get your hands up their skirt every morning.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.92,0:30:29.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,, 晚上给她们唱着小曲\N{\fscx070\fscy070} You serenade them every night.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.79,0:30:32.95,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你该不是爱上那些600磅的反刍动物了吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}That,or you're in love with a 600-pounder who likes to chew her vomit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.02,0:30:37.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我在那做什么吗 -做什么\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- You know what I'm really doin' up there,Richie? - What's that?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.10,0:30:39.03,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,做你老妈\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Your mother.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.34,0:30:51.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么回事啊 老兄\N{\fscx070\fscy070}What's your problem,man?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.88,0:31:01.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,嘿!嘿!\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Hey! Hey!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.55,0:31:04.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,别打了 你到底怎么了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Stop it! What's the matter with you?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.09,0:31:06.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,行了 站起来 我们走吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Come on. Get up. Let's go. Let's go.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.26,0:31:10.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 你别闹了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Hey,hey! You can quit right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.46,0:31:12.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,给我住手\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Right now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.87,0:31:15.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我不干了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I quit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.44,0:31:20.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你不能退出 这不是工作 这是判决 见鬼\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You can't quit. It isn't a job. It's a sentence! God.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.77,0:31:23.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-让我跟那孩子谈 - 不 不 \N{\fscx070\fscy070}- I'll talk with that kid. - No,no! Earl.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.54,0:31:26.41,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,先等等 让他走 让他冷静一下\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Just wait. Let him go. Let him cool off,okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.48,0:31:28.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你看着我 你知道该怎么做\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You. Look at me. You know better.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.98,0:31:30.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,现在去卡车那里\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Go to the truck. Now.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.04,0:31:57.06,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Albert 你下周二要懂得这段弹奏好吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Albert. I expect you to know that piece by next Tuesday. Okay.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.14,0:32:01.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-好的 - 好 你可以走了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Okay. - Okay. Get outta here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.79,0:32:10.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,来坐下\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Come and sit.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.92,0:32:16.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,老爸已经教训过我了 所以\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Dad already gave me an earful,so,uh...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.46,0:32:21.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得怎么弹吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You still remember how to play?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.14,0:32:31.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,音乐一直都是属于我们的 对吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Music's always been our thing,hasn't it?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.78,0:32:33.71,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你和我\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You and me?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.42,0:32:39.35,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,它一直是我们属于我们的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}It'll always be something we share.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.22,0:32:48.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你觉得Kelly真的很幸运\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I imagine you think Kelley's real lucky.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.19,0:32:50.59,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,家里那么有钱\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Gets to have all that money.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.66,0:32:52.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,看起来拥有了全世界\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Seems to have the whole world in his hands.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.00,0:32:57.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你有没有想过自己很幸福呢\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Ever consider maybe you're the lucky one?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.11,0:33:04.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,在法庭上我都没有看到他妈妈\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I didn't see a mother in that courtroom.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.99,0:33:26.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了它\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- - You killed him.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.07,0:33:29.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,杀了谁 你到底在讲什么\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Killed who? What are you talkin' about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.07,0:33:30.93,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你就直接把他扔垃圾箱了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You just threw him in the garbage!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.00,0:33:35.00,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,他对你做了什么你要这样-你说那只老鼠吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- What did he ever do to you? - Are we talkin' about the mouse?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.07,0:33:37.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你这个混蛋 我再也不想跟你讲话了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You're just a jerk. I'm never speaking to you again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.69,0:33:53.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我无法忍受这附近了 连件漂亮衣服都买不着\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I'm just so sick of not being able to buy good clothes around here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.69,0:33:55.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你下星期想不想去波士顿\N{\fscx070\fscy070}So,you want to come to Boston next week?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.77,0:34:07.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我很热\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I'm hot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.81,0:34:10.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我想喝些东西\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I need to go get something to drink.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.93,0:34:29.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我姐姐不喜欢你\N{\fscx070\fscy070}My sister hates you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.99,0:34:31.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 她都不了解我\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Why? She doesn't even know me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.36,0:34:35.66,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 她讨厌你是出于原则上的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Well,she hates you on principle.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.73,0:34:38.43,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴不是针对个人的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I'm glad it's not personal.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.78,0:34:46.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,这又是怎么了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}What was that about?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.74,0:34:49.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我杀死了Ralph\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I killed Ralph.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.85,0:34:53.61,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,哦应该把你逮捕起来\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Oh. You could get arrested for that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.69,0:34:56.09,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,有手铐么\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Will there be handcuffs?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.92,0:35:01.19,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你想被拷起来\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Do you want handcuffs?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.36,0:35:04.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,那要看拷我的人是谁咯\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Depends on who's puttin' them on.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.36,0:35:07.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,可能是警长哦 所以别高兴的太早了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Probably the sheriff,so don't get too excited.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.37,0:35:13.89,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你约会时还带着警长吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Do you always bring the sheriff on dates?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.71,0:35:19.40,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,只要我没犯法就用不着了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Not if I'm the one who's breaking the law.{\r}
