Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.19,1:08:23.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,也就那么回事 只是个干扰罢了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}That's what it is. Just a distraction.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.19,1:08:25.13,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,那不是你的生活\N{\fscx070\fscy070}It's not your life.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.70,1:08:29.46,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,以后你还有更重要的事情\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You have much bigger things ahead of you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.53,1:08:32.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,该是向前看齐的时候了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Now get your eyes forward,already.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.37,1:08:37.36,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你现在是不是还要赶公车呢\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I think you have a bus to catch.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.34,1:09:10.90,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得你自己在干什么\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- So what is it you think you're doing?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.97,1:09:14.34,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-你到底在做什么 -我不知道\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- What is it that you think I'm doing? - I don't know.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.41,1:09:16.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,不管你在做什么 该停止了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- But whatever it is,it is gonna stop! - [Phone Ringing]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.85,1:09:18.81,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,停止什么 你知道他是什么样的人\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- What's gonna stop? - You know what he is!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.88,1:09:20.82,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,不 你根本不了解他  你要接电话吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- No. And you have no idea what he is! - Will you get the phone?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.88,1:09:23.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你没从你姐那吸取教训吗 我又不是Jen\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Didn't you learn from your sister? - I'm not Jen.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.52,1:09:25.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-我在做之前清楚得很\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- I'm walking into this with my eyes open.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.01,1:09:26.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你知道自己在做什么吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- What is it you're walking into?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.12,1:09:28.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,跟一个孩子的感情纠葛\N{\fscx070\fscy070}A relationship... with this kid?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.52,1:09:29.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,再过几个星期他就走了 \N{\fscx070\fscy070}He's gonna be gone in a few weeks.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.76,1:09:31.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你将再也不会见到他\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You're not gonna hear from him again.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.06,1:09:33.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-也许他跟别人不同-说来听听\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Well,maybe he's different. - Tell me how.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.60,1:09:36.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-也许他爱着我-他都不懂什么是爱\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Maybe he loves me. - He doesn't know the meaning of the word!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.37,1:09:40.23,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-你不了解他 -Falco医生的电话\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- And you don't know him -That was Dr. Falco's office.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.30,1:09:41.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-他怎么说的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- What did he want?.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.44,1:09:45.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想要确认你明天的预约\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- He wanted to confirm your appointment for tomorrow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.21,1:09:48.37,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-他们说跟你谈过了 你为什么不告诉我们\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- They said they talked to you. Why didn't you tell us?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.37,1:09:50.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,, -因为我不会去\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- - 'Cause I'm not going.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.28,1:09:53.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 因为我没事 我的膝盖也没事\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Why? - Because I'm fine. And my knee is fine.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.98,1:09:56.92,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,一切都很好 而且我不想再谈论了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}And it's been fine. And I'm sick of talking about it!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.76,1:10:04.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Samantha!\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Samantha!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.07,1:10:15.63,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我来找Samantha\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I'm looking for Samantha.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.70,1:10:17.70,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我没见到她\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I haven't seen her.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.34,1:10:22.67,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,那好 如果你见到她的话\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Well,if you see her,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.75,1:10:25.27,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,就告诉她快点回家\N{\fscx070\fscy070}just tell her it's important she come home.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:26.45,1:10:29.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,算我求你了 Kelly\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Look,I'm asking,Kelley.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.08,1:10:31.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,好吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.41,1:11:00.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,一切都还好吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Is everything okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.85,1:11:03.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.85,1:11:08.62,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这地方\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I love this spot.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.36,1:11:15.69,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,就像是地球上的天堂\N{\fscx070\fscy070}It's like heaven... right here on earth.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:15.76,1:11:18.73,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,也许天堂就是这样的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Maybe that's what heaven is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.80,1:11:22.86,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,也许有着我们这一生挚爱的人们与地方\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Maybe we go through life collecting people and places we love.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.04,1:11:27.24,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,就是我们的天堂\N{\fscx070\fscy070}And they become our heaven.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.31,1:11:30.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你的母亲就在那里\N{\fscx070\fscy070}And that's where your mom is.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.28,1:11:34.84,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,在天堂里被她所爱的事物围绕着\N{\fscx070\fscy070}She's in her heaven surrounded by everything that she loves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.92,1:11:39.85,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,包括你\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Including you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.92,1:11:43.65,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-你这么觉得吗 -是啊\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- You think so? - Yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.80,1:11:54.74,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,来赛跑吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Let's race.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:57.27,1:11:59.64,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx070\fscy070}Sam...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.11,1:12:36.54,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-Samantha\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Samantha!{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.61,1:12:39.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 你没事吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}What happened? Are you okay?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:42.55,1:12:45.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}So,what's the matter?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.59,1:12:50.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,- Samantha,发生什么了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Samantha,what is it? {\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.16,1:12:52.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我得告诉你一些事\N{\fscx070\fscy070}There's something I have to tell you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.14,1:13:12.17,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,天哪 那是怎么从她的腿转移到肝脏的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Boy,how does it go from her leg to her liver?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.25,1:13:14.55,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,骨肉瘤就是这么转移的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}That's how osteosarcoma works.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:14.62,1:13:16.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我们一直都知道有这个可能性\N{\fscx070\fscy070}We always knew that this was a possibility.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.05,1:13:18.99,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,那我们能做什么\N{\fscx070\fscy070}What can we do?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.05,1:13:21.08,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我希望还有其他治疗手段能提供给你们\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I wish there was a list of options I could give you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.08,1:13:22.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在已经没有办法了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}but there just isn't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.06,1:13:24.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,只是它转移得太快了\N{\fscx070\fscy070} It just moved so fast.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.78,1:13:40.87,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx070\fscy070}Sam.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.08,1:13:45.01,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,嗨\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Hey.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.08,1:13:48.21,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我出去走走 一会儿回来\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I'm gonna go for a walk. I'll be back in a minute.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.46,1:13:58.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,来 坐在我旁边\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Come and sit with me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.01,1:14:21.48,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx070\fscy070}Kelley...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:22.95,1:14:25.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,当你跟别人说你得了癌症\N{\fscx070\fscy070}When you tell someone you have cancer,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.89,1:14:31.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,不管你怎么说的 他们只是感到很遗憾而已\N{\fscx070\fscy070}no matter how you say it,they just end up feeling sorry for you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.76,1:14:36.16,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不希望你为我感到遗憾\N{\fscx070\fscy070}And I didn't want you feeling sorry for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.43,1:14:40.56,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你会死吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Could you die from this?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.80,1:14:45.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我会的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I am gonna die from this.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.91,1:14:50.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,他们没有治疗的办法吗 嗯\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- There's... There's nothing that they can do for you? - Sure,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.51,1:14:52.38,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,他们还有一些方法可以治疗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}there are things they can do.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.45,1:14:55.44,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,但那对我来说不合适\N{\fscx070\fscy070}They're just not the right things for me.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.52,1:14:58.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-但只要能治你的病 -不可能的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- But if they can save you... - Won't.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.52,1:15:01.42,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,癌细胞已经转移了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}It's already spread.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.49,1:15:03.96,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,即使是用他们能提供的最好治疗方法\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Even with the treatment,the best they can offer...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.03,1:15:06.79,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我顶多能活一到两年\N{\fscx070\fscy070}is a chance I could live a year or two.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.86,1:15:10.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,太不值得了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}It's not worth it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.00,1:15:18.20,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎样 你就这么放弃了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}So,what? You just gonna give up?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.91,1:15:24.88,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你就这么死去吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You just gonna die?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.95,1:15:28.58,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fscx070\fscy070}No.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:28.65,1:15:32.45,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我会活下去\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I'm going to live.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.72,1:15:37.18,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,不只是你\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Just not as long as you.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:00.85,1:16:04.29,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,来看看这些东西\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Come look at this stuff.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:04.35,1:16:08.02,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,在 Ridge路的一个老地方看到的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}- Found it at an old place out on Ridge Road.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.09,1:16:10.52,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,噢 是吗\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Oh,yeah.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.59,1:16:13.15,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,Jasper,Kelley 来这里\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Jasper,Kelley,come here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.23,1:16:18.39,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,-这是英格兰松木 很好很柔软\N{\fscx070\fscy070}-This,uh,English pine... nice and soft.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.47,1:16:20.80,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,看看 这个用来刻字很不错的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Good for carving. Look at that.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.87,1:16:24.83,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,[我们不会迷失方向]\N{\fscx070\fscy070}[Music] We won't lose track [music]{\r}
