Dialogue: 0,1:16:38.15,1:16:41.68,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,[无法难解释他们的坠落]\N{\fscx070\fscy070}[Music] Why they fall it's hard to tell [music]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.76,1:16:44.28,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,[有一些事情]\N{\fscx070\fscy070}[Music]But some things you can't [music]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.36,1:16:47.95,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,[你无法买卖]\N{\fscx070\fscy070}[Music]Buy or sell [music]{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.10,1:16:54.33,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,[我们只会伤害我们的所爱]\N{\fscx070\fscy070}[Music] Yeah,we only hurt the ones we love [music]{\r}
