Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.81,1:17:41.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,那挺好的   对吧\N{\fscx070\fscy070}It's good,right?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.85,1:17:43.78,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,是挺好的\N{\fscx070\fscy070}It's great.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.99,1:17:52.98,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx070\fscy070}Jas?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.06,1:17:55.12,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上……\N{\fscx070\fscy070}About that night?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.20,1:17:57.76,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,噢\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Oh.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.83,1:18:00.53,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我们没必要提了\N{\fscx070\fscy070}We don't have to talk about it.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.50,1:18:04.77,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我只想说很抱歉\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Just wanted to say that I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.84,1:18:09.30,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,呃……我也很抱歉\N{\fscx070\fscy070}Well... I'm sorry.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.38,1:18:12.47,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你抱歉什么\N{\fscx070\fscy070}What do you have to be sorry for?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.55,1:18:15.04,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,我不是个很好的朋友\N{\fscx070\fscy070}I haven't been a very good friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.85,1:18:21.91,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你一直是我最好的朋友\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You've been my best friend.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.99,1:18:24.72,*Default,说话人,0000,0000,0000,,你永远是我最好的朋友\N{\fscx070\fscy070}You'll always be my best friend.{\r}
